WEBVTT

00:01:56.331 --> 00:02:00.359
Semizlik ko'pincha energiya 
nomutanosibligidan kelib chiqadi.

00:02:00.359 --> 00:02:03.135
Agar kaloriyadan hosil bo'lgan 
energiya miqdori

00:02:03.135 --> 00:02:06.574
jismoniy faoliyatga sarflangan 
energiya miqdoridan ko'p bo'lsa,

00:02:06.574 --> 00:02:10.286
organizm ortiqcha kaloriyani 
yog' shaklida saqlay boshlaydi.

00:02:10.286 --> 00:02:14.455
Ko'p hollarda bu nomutanosiblik 
turli shart-sharoit va

00:02:14.455 --> 00:02:16.479
inson tanlovi natijasida yuzaga keladi.

00:02:16.479 --> 00:02:21.113
Kattalar jismoniy mashg'ulotlarga 
haftasiga kamida 2,5 soat,

00:02:21.113 --> 00:02:23.756
bolalar esa kuniga bir soatdan 
vaqt ajratishlari kerak.

00:02:23.756 --> 00:02:28.133
Ammo dunyo bo'ylab har to'rt
kishidan bittasi va har o'nta boladan

00:02:28.133 --> 00:02:29.856
sakkiztasi jismonan nofaol.

00:02:29.856 --> 00:02:33.474
Kaloriyaga boy tayyor ovqatlar, 
ular hajmining ko'payishi hamda keng